{"tid":1062743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特区政府申撥款設大湾區發展專員　月薪 26 萬　助理專員月薪 19 萬","createTime":"2019-03-15T09:43:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T10:45:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"84a73200dbf94ff4a39a5e1fdd93cec7c3f7cc19","tid":1062743,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/bayman-08_6LNVl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fbayman-08_6LNVl_1200x0.png&h=4559368f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京上月公布《粵港澳大灣區發展規劃大綱》，政制及內地事務局建議，成立粵港澳大灣區發展辦公室，加強港府和內地聯絡協調，制定和統籌港府參與大灣區建設策略等，政制局又建議，在辦公室開設首長級職位「粵港澳大灣區發展專員」，屬首長級薪級點第 6 點，月薪 260,600 元；另外亦建議增設大灣區發展助理專員，月薪 187,150 元，預計兩名專員年薪開支合共 530 萬。<br />\n<br />\n根據政制局向工商事務委員會提交文件，新設的粵港澳大灣區發展辦公室，建議開設的專員和肋理專員兩個編外職位為期四年，另外亦將會在 2019-20 年度，開設 17 個非首長級職位，為期四年，支援專員和助理專員工作，年薪開支總額 1,240 萬元；換言之粵港澳大灣區發展辦公室，單是薪金開支一年將達 1,770 萬元。<br />\n<br />\n而在較早前公布的財政預算案，財政司司長陳茂波宣布預留 1.11 億元，設立粵港澳大灣區發展辦公室，他強調辦公室有需要，以推動香港把握大灣區發展機遇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%94%B3%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E8%A8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1-%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-26-%E8%90%AC-%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-19-%E8%90%AC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA-26-%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA-19-%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsac5Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=082d0792\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%2594%25B3%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA-26-%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2588%25E8%2596%25AA-19-%25E8%2590%25AC%2F&h=d4af56f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%94%B3%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE%E8%A8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1-%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-26-%E8%90%AC-%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E5%B0%88%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%88%E8%96%AA-19-%E8%90%AC/</a>"},{"pid":"f4967363094bee4a4a134b35c4cb8818d90f41f3","tid":1062743,"uid":174752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"比自己人"},{"pid":"e65c7e1223fef5ea34923a090a1f2bd7451cecbc","tid":1062743,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:45:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}